channel.title: People cant play, but i can?! HELP!
channel.description:
Hello, all.
I have a server called Simmonscape. I was sooo happy when it said "simmonscape.no-ip.biz running on port 43594" I tried going on my server, when it said "error connecting to server" But, when i put my defult ip in for the ip (127.0.0.1) it connected and the server was running, I have simmonscape.no-ip.biz on my no-ip duc and i portforwarded, but i cannot seem to run the server on simmonscape.no-ip.biz. PLEASE HELP ME!
I know that people are supposed to connect to my server ip, but nothing is happening!
Please helpppp!
